Ic
Ice Cream

Our ice cream base is crafted with fresh, premium cream sourced from local dairies, ensuring the highest quality and supporting our community. We pride ourselves on a unique 'cow to cup time' of less than 14 days, meaning from the moment the cow is milked to when you savor it in your cup, it's always incredibly fresh. This dedication results in a velvety smooth texture that elevates every flavor.
